de.wagnst.tpe.exercises.exercise2.master

Class Currency

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.wagnst.tpe.exercises.exercise2.master.Currency

  • public final class Currency
extends java.lang.Object
    Currency manages special operations on existing Currencies. Every Currency has a name, code, exchange rate and an information if it got a subunit

    New instances can be created with the help of the constructor 

         Currency currency = new Currency("Dollar", "$", 10000, true);

    Objects of this class are immutable. The methods don't change the state of their object, but return a new object.

    Author:
    maxGross, wagnst
